deterioro renal, malformaciones\\Nrenales, oligohidramnios, insuficiencia placentaria) (n¹).","guid":"-1XfC_KRKc-mUSSqs7J_4Q","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"143","text":"Lactancia","guid":"uuXpXuLeuoFAK32MoSuXaA","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"142","text":"Relativas","guid":"c3RCYWvcvgTJ45ddr5CZTQ","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"Estenosis aórtica","guid":"7G6xC-xyd2PWJj71ClI35Q","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"Disfunción renal → Ajustar dosis si FG < 60 mL/min (n¹²,¹³).","guid":"eYLRlnIWPp0FiZSOdCiLnw","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"Estenosis bilateral de la arteria renal o riñón único → ↓FG puede causar lesión renal aguda.","guid":"gakJGUVXb3beJZ7jsVUHSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"142","text":"Interacciones","guid":"CUNZs4foOElBuuRVP5Q8cg","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"Otros antihipertensivos → ↑ efecto hipotensor","guid":"cU4Mym26xPBH4zLsAAQi8Q","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"AINEs → ↓ efecto antihipertensivo","guid":"XiWOAibdAvRQ_DZSjnPD9A","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"Diuréticos ahorradores de potasio u otros fármacos que ↑ potasio → ↑ riesgo de hiperkalemia","guid":"905v2NjApkF63-NNlPNSIg","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"Litio → ↑ niveles por ↓ eliminación renal","guid":"f5a67vn8MbH3IliAlGBjbg","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"Alopurinol → ↑ riesgo de reacciones inmunológicas o leucopenia (n¹⁵,¹⁶)","guid":"5CL2LVgPfXWPL8QEUyg6tQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"141","text":"Interacciones de inhibidores\\Ndirectos de renina:","guid":"oVBwnL6ljpB4CYjSgD89Gg","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"Inhibidores de P-gp (ej. ketoconazol, verapamilo, claritromicina, eritromicina, amiodarona)\\N→ ↑ niveles de aliskiren","guid":"EdBqXAFbTP4nn9B07XJuTg","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"IECA o BRA → ↑ hiperkalemia (n¹⁸)","guid":"cFZ3NBUzYKn6VwB0QoOAyw","children":[]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"141","text":"→ No combinar con IECA o BRA, especialmente en\\Npacientes con DM o enfermedad renal preexistente.","guid":"M8dIPYCwDbkYm7XGqb2i1Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\Nadicionales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"Iniciar con dosis bajas (preferentemente en ambiente controlado) para evitar hipotensión severa (n¹³).","guid":"O4-w9AfCbgLnOynl-vV0Lg","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"Combinar IECA o BRA con diuréticos tiazídicos para contrarrestar los riesgos de hiperkalemia e hipokalemia.","guid":"75DNaSVwBn0azUHA8D3s_w","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"162","text":"Al iniciar IECA o BRA, monitorizar PA, potasio y creatinina.","guid":"v9V2EHXTlNQj0EEowG5kxw","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":165,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Sistema renina angiotensina aldosterona-2024","id":"map_866","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Sistema renina angiotensina aldosterona-2024"}